    {
      "id": "6a1b417d0000000000f915de",
      "text": "[sta.icon]向上心が強く自己客観視に長け、承認欲求と謙虚さの間で誠実に揺れている求道者タイプ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780171134,
      "updated": 1780171193
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1b417e0000000000f915e0",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/35fd5a8822e2c7af62e7219d74926dd7]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780171135,
      "updated": 1780171304
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1b6a4a00000000003a69e0",
      "text": " なんかかっこいい[takker.icon][kana.icon]",
      "userId": "5e9487d750011b001eb536eb",
      "created": 1780181579,
      "updated": 1780204267
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1b7b820000000000959dfd",
      "text": " [ススクソッ]ってなんだよ[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1780185987,
      "updated": 1780187456
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1b969500000000008cadb3",
      "text": " グラブルっぽさある[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780192917,
      "updated": 1780192922
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1b811c00000000003337e1",
      "text": " どうやっても微妙に使いづらそうな高さの机いい[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780187421,
      "updated": 1780205350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bc72600000000003f7389",
      "text": "  わろた[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780205350,
      "updated": 1780205353
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1ba48d0000000000f7e70f",
      "text": "\tひらめぎ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780196494,
      "updated": 1780209278
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1d20770000000000b7aedf",
      "text": "\t[ひらめきは足の裏からやってくる]、いつか使いたい（いつだ）[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780293752,
      "updated": 1780293792
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bd67a0000000000f500d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780209276,
      "updated": 1780209276
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bb9790000000000419bf3",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780201849,
      "updated": 1780201850
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bb97a0000000000419bf5",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/635d43a489310f3eef83e1b7eb794c1f]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780201850,
      "updated": 1780201853
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bb97d0000000000419bf6",
      "text": "\t\t謎空間になった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780201853,
      "updated": 1780201863
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bbeff0000000000ca683b",
      "text": "\t\t当初もっと古い家で囲炉裏があったのだが、「現代風にして」としたところやかんを引っ掛けるフック付きの机が爆誕した",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780203264,
      "updated": 1780203572
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bcb5c0000000000d97842",
      "text": "\t\t ？？？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780206418,
      "updated": 1780206421
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bb98c0000000000419bf7",
      "text": "\t\t「イラスト」と指定しないと写真みたいになって謎のおじさんが出てきたので却下",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780201868,
      "updated": 1780201883
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bc3080000000000af3ff2",
      "text": "\t\t和やかでいいかんじ[kana.icon][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780204297,
      "updated": 1780206427
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bcb720000000000d97843",
      "text": "\t\tさりげなくマイコン置いてあるのすき[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780206440,
      "updated": 1780206450
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bec7700000000006f15ae",
      "text": "\t\tこれになりたい[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780214910,
      "updated": 1780214910
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bb97a0000000000419bf4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780201850,
      "updated": 1780201850
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c03d300000000007be892",
      "text": "\tExport for AIの邪魔をしないように URLリンクにしてみる[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780220883,
      "updated": 1780220889
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c02fb00000000008e134b",
      "text": "\t試しに作った作品[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780220667,
      "updated": 1780220678
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c031e00000000008e134c",
      "text": "\t\t[井戸端荘: 冷蔵庫の運用ポリシー・クライシス https://scrapbox.io/villagepump/%E4%BA%95%E6%88%B8%E7%AB%AF%E8%8D%98:_%E5%86%B7%E8%94%B5%E5%BA%AB%E3%81%AE%E9%81%8B%E7%94%A8%E3%83%9D%E3%83%AA%E3%82%B7%E3%83%BC%E3%83%BB%E3%82%AF%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%82%B7%E3%82%B9] ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780220702,
      "updated": 1780220879
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1be8d30000000000419c34",
      "text": "\t他にもプロットを考えてもらった[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780213971,
      "updated": 1780220849
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1be90a0000000000419c52",
      "text": "\t\t[井戸端荘: 様々なプロット(inajob) https://scrapbox.io/villagepump/%E4%BA%95%E6%88%B8%E7%AB%AF%E8%8D%98:_%E6%A7%98%E3%80%85%E3%81%AA%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%83%E3%83%88(inajob)]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780214026,
      "updated": 1780220849
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1becc500000000006f15b1",
      "text": "\t自分中心につくってみた[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780214982,
      "updated": 1780261354
    },
